					  Thanks for a Great 2011 Tournament Season  

					 by Allen Freeman  |  November 9, 2011    1 Comment  

					 

 With the start of November, it’s time to call it a season and wind down on 2011. 
 To the tournament players of Northeast Ohio, to the ‘executive directors’ of the golf events run throughout the area, and to the readers of this website who don’t play at a competitive level but simply want to keep up with tournament golf in Greater Cleveland — thanks once again for sharing another great golf season right here on NEOHgolf.com.   [Read more ?]  

					 

   	




